OL,3,CKillamarsh killer handed another life
OL,4,Csentence for prison hammer attack
OL,6,FA former cage fighter serving a whole-
OL,7,Flife tariff for murdering his pregnant
OL,8,Fpartner and three children has been
OL,9,Fhanded a further life sentence for a
OL,10,Fhammer attack on a fellow inmate at a
OL,11,Fmaximum security prison.
OL,13,FDamien Bendall, 36, was sentenced at
OL,14,FTeesside Crown Court for the attempted
OL,15,Fmurder of Michael Mullaney at HMP
OL,16,FFrankland, Durham, after smashing him
OL,17,Ffour times in the head with a claw
OL,18,Fhammer without warning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
