CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771952662
OL,3,CKillamarsh killer handed another life
OL,4,Csentence for prison hammer attack
OL,6,FBendall had planned the attack to
OL,7,Fengineer a move to segregation unit
OL,8,Fbecause he was concerned that his
OL,9,Fmental state was deteriorating,
OL,10,FVanessa Marshall KC, defending, said.
OL,12,FShe said Bendall wanted to apologise
OL,13,Fto Mr Mullaney, saying: "He held no
OL,14,Fcontempt for Mr Mullaney, despite what
OL,15,Fhe did.
OL,17,F"There is evidence that they were
OL,18,Ffriends and he wanted to convey his
OL,19,Fregrets and apologies."
OL,26,@uD@YOUyD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
