OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771952662
OL,3,CKillamarsh killer handed another life
OL,4,Csentence for prison hammer attack
OL,6,FJudge Francis Laird KC said the
OL,7,Fsentence was life with a minimum term
OL,8,Fof 15 years, but that Bendall will
OL,9,Fnever be released in any event.
OL,11,FHe said the attempted murder was
OL,12,Faggravated because it happened in
OL,13,Fprison and due to his "previous
OL,14,Fconvictions for the most serious
OL,15,Fviolent and sexual offences".
OL,26,@uD@WOUwD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
