OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771952662
OL,3,CKillamarsh killer handed another life
OL,4,Csentence for prison hammer attack
OL,6,FFormer cage-fighter Bendall murdered
OL,7,Fpregnant Terri Harris, 35, her
OL,8,Fchildren ` 11-year-old Lacey and 13-
OL,9,Fyear-old John Paul ` and Lacey's
OL,10,Ffriend, 11-year-old Connie Gent, in
OL,11,FChandos Crescent, Killamarsh,
OL,12,FDerbyshire, on September 19 2021.
OL,14,FHe was given a whole-life order in
OL,15,FDecember 2022.
OL,17,FHe used a claw hammer to carry out the
OL,18,Fprolonged attacks at the home he
OL,19,Fshared with Ms Harris.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
