OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771952662
OL,3,CKillamarsh killer handed another life
OL,4,Csentence for prison hammer attack
OL,6,FHe also admitted to raping Lacey as
OL,7,Fshe was dying.
OL,9,FBendall, in a blue T-shirt and with a
OL,10,Fshaved head, watched the proceedings
OL,11,Fvia a videolink from HMP Wakefield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
